will not come to pass.

48
00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:09,700
Eighth Prince?

49
00:03:10,220 --> 00:03:11,180
[Nangong Pin]

50
00:03:11,180 --> 00:03:11,980
[Nangong Pin]
Mr. Zhou.

51
00:03:11,980 --> 00:03:15,500
Tell me, what is the way
of being a ruler?

52
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:19,660
The way of being a ruler.

53
00:03:20,780 --> 00:03:22,940
Are you referring to being a husband?

54
00:03:24,620 --> 00:03:26,380
In terms of how one
should behave as a husband,

55
00:03:27,100 --> 00:03:29,020
well, it mainly depends
on whom you marry.

56
00:03:29,620 --> 00:03:31,180
If you marry
a beautiful and gentle lady,

57
00:03:31,180 --> 00:03:32,500
