58
00:03:33,060 --> 00:03:36,500
But if you marry a shrew, then, well...

59
00:03:38,820 --> 00:03:40,020
Ridiculous.

60
00:03:40,620 --> 00:03:42,780
Mr. Zhou, am I wrong?

61
00:03:43,780 --> 00:03:45,980
The way of a husband and wife
is a part of human relationships

62
00:03:46,180 --> 00:03:47,740
and everyone has to get married.

63
00:03:48,140 --> 00:03:49,780
I heard that several female students

64
00:03:49,780 --> 00:03:51,420
arrived at the Chongwen Academy today.

65
00:03:51,420 --> 00:03:53,940
Mr. Zhou, won't you
take us to meet them?

66
00:03:54,220 --> 00:03:56,220
I'm truly infuriated.

67
00:03:56,540 --> 00:03:57,460
Ladies,

68
00:03:57,460 --> 00:03:59,420
we've arrived
at the Chongwen Academy in the palace.

69
00:03:59,420 --> 00:04:00,100
From now on,

70
00:04:00,100 --> 00:04:01,380
- you'll be studying here.
- Once you enter the Chongwen Academy,

71
00:04:01,380 --> 00:04:02,860
pay even more attention
to your manners and etiquette.

72
00:04:02,860 --> 00:04:03,700
Take a good look around.

73
00:04:03,700 --> 00:04:04,740
Got it.

74
00:04:05,020 --> 00:04:06,420
I'll familiarize myself
with the surroundings first,

75
00:04:06,420 --> 00:04:08,180
then figure out a way
to sneak out and steal the pearls later.

76
00:04:08,340 --> 00:04:09,340
Once we're in the palace,

77
00:04:09,340 --> 00:04:11,700
will we be able to see
His Highness the Crown Prince often?

78
00:04:12,300 --> 00:04:13,860
His Highness is of noble status

79
00:04:13,860 --> 00:04:15,580
and probably wouldn't bother
with us insignificant figures.

80
00:04:15,580 --> 00:04:17,260
Plus, with a talented lady
like Mei Yushan around,

81
00:04:17,260 --> 00:04:18,940
His Highness might not even notice us.

82
00:04:18,940 --> 00:04:20,020
That's not necessarily true.

83
00:04:20,020 --> 00:04:21,380
The other day at the museum,

84
00:04:21,380 --> 00:04:22,980
His Highness
didn't even spare her a glance.

85
00:04:22,980 --> 00:04:24,100
Greetings, ladies.

86
00:04:24,260 --> 00:04:25,860
- Greetings, Your Highnesses.
- Greetings, Your Highnesses.

87
00:04:27,420 --> 00:04:28,500
In the future, we'll be classmates,

88
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:29,260
no need to be so formal.

89
00:04:29,980 --> 00:04:31,580
Do any of you gentlemen know

90
00:04:31,580 --> 00:04:34,060
when the Crown Prince
will visit the Chongwen Academy?

91
00:04:35,260 --> 00:04:37,380
Yao has been deeply involved
in court affairs in recent years

92
00:04:37,380 --> 00:04:38,660
and hasn't visited
the Chongwen Academy for a long time.

93
00:04:39,940 --> 00:04:42,540
