you ladies will be disappointed.

94
00:04:44,580 --> 00:04:46,380
How could this be?

95
00:04:47,700 --> 00:04:48,300
Your Highness.

96
00:04:48,700 --> 00:04:49,580
His Highness?

97
00:04:50,980 --> 00:04:52,060
Your Highness!

98
00:05:05,620 --> 00:05:06,940
Who pushed us?

99
00:05:08,700 --> 00:05:10,260
Your Highness, you are leaving already?

100
00:05:12,540 --> 00:05:13,260
Your Highness...

101
00:05:14,860 --> 00:05:15,780
Your Highness, don't...

102
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:21,100
- Greetings, Your Highness.
- Greetings, Your Highness.

103
00:05:22,140 --> 00:05:23,620
Yao, how come you are here?

104
00:05:24,660 --> 00:05:26,060
- Your Highness.
- Your Highness.

105
00:05:26,060 --> 00:05:27,980
The Crown Prince will be visiting
the Chongwen Academy in the coming days

106
00:05:27,980 --> 00:05:29,260
to study with everyone.

107
00:05:29,420 --> 00:05:30,180
- For real?
- Really?

108
00:05:32,220 --> 00:05:33,620
- That's great!
- That's great!

109
00:05:37,220 --> 00:05:38,500
Ladies,

110
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:40,620
this is the Grand Tutor
of our Chongwen Academy.

111
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:42,780
- Greetings, sir.
- Greetings, sir.

112
00:05:44,940 --> 00:05:48,460
With the Crown Prince
returning to the Chongwen Academy

113
00:05:49,340 --> 00:05:51,500
and the arrival of the young ladies,

114
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:53,180
I can see that none of you

115
00:05:53,180 --> 00:05:55,220
have much interest in studying today.

116
00:05:58,300 --> 00:05:59,180
Let's go.

117
00:06:01,220 --> 00:06:02,170
We are so fortunate
to have the opportunity

118
00:06:02,170 --> 00:06:02,780
to meet His Highness today.

119
00:06:02,780 --> 00:06:03,540
Indeed.

120
00:06:06,740 --> 00:06:07,560
Ladies, please come and collect

121
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,660
your student identity plates
for the academy.

122
00:06:09,220 --> 00:06:10,660
- Sure.
- Let's go.

123
00:06:22,340 --> 00:06:23,820
You sure ran away quickly yesterday,
didn't you?

124
00:06:24,500 --> 00:06:27,220
Yao, it's great that you're back
at the Chongwen Academy.

125
00:06:27,220 --> 00:06:28,580
Now I get to see you every day.

126
00:06:31,260 --> 00:06:31,940
Could it be...?

127
00:06:32,420 --> 00:06:33,060
Right?

128
00:06:33,380 --> 00:06:35,500
Ladies, please come and collect
your student identity plates.

129
00:06:37,900 --> 00:06:39,260
Have you been doing
your homework lately?

130
00:06:39,540 --> 00:06:40,660
The Grand Tutor just tested you

131
00:06:40,660 --> 00:06:41,740
on what it means to be a ruler.

132
00:06:41,740 --> 00:06:42,580
Let's hear your answer.

133
00:06:42,580 --> 00:06:43,700
- Yes.
- Go ahead and tell us.

134
00:06:43,700 --> 00:06:44,660
Let's hear your answer.

135
00:06:44,660 --> 00:06:45,860
Yao, you're the Crown Prince,

136
00:06:46,420 --> 00:06:47,480
bearing heavy responsibilities.

137
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,980
Naturally, your considerations
are different.

138
00:06:49,740 --> 00:06:51,340
As for me,
I'm just a mere Eighth Prince.

139
00:06:51,980 --> 00:06:53,580
What does being a ruler
have to do with me?

140
00:06:53,580 --> 00:06:54,460
What number
is the Crown Prince's plate?

141
00:06:54,460 --> 00:06:55,500
I can't see the number clearly.

142
00:06:55,500 --> 00:06:56,260
[Two]
Number two.

143
00:06:56,260 --> 00:06:56,300
[Two]

144
00:06:56,300 --> 00:06:57,220
Where's number three?

145
00:06:57,420 --> 00:06:59,300
The Eighth Prince
is quicker than all of you.

146
00:06:59,300 --> 00:06:59,940
Why can't I find it?

147
00:06:59,940 --> 00:07:02,260
He's already seated
next to the Crown Prince.

148
00:07:02,260 --> 00:07:03,950
[One]

149
00:07:05,940 --> 00:07:07,860
They've taken numbers one and three.

150
00:07:08,740 --> 00:07:10,220
What's the point for us
to choose the other ones?

151
00:07:11,180 --> 00:07:12,540
His Highness likes symmetry,

152
00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:14,820
so we can't sit on either side of him.

153
00:07:16,540 --> 00:07:17,540
That won't do.

154
00:07:17,540 --> 00:07:19,220
I still need to ask him for the pearl.

155
00:07:20,220 --> 00:07:22,220
Then let's sit on either side
of the Crown Prince.

156
00:07:22,220 --> 00:07:22,860
No way.

157
00:07:26,220 --> 00:07:27,020
Eunuch Song.

158
00:07:27,500 --> 00:07:28,100
What is it?

159
00:07:28,100 --> 00:07:31,420
Is it true that once we enter
the academy, there's no hierarchy

160
00:07:31,540 --> 00:07:33,580
and we have to follow
the rules of the academy?

161
00:07:34,620 --> 00:07:37,060
That has been the rule
of the Chongwen Academy for many years.

162
00:07:37,540 --> 00:07:40,020
Is it a rule that no one
can sit next to the Crown Prince?

163
00:07:40,660 --> 00:07:42,060
Well...

164
00:07:42,700 --> 00:07:43,980
No,

165
00:07:47,300 --> 00:07:48,500
