166
00:07:49,380 --> 00:07:51,340
Since Eunuch Song says there isn't,

167
00:07:51,460 --> 00:07:52,860
I'll sit next to him.

168
00:07:54,740 --> 00:07:56,900
How can you sit here?

169
00:07:56,940 --> 00:07:57,860
- Get up!
- Get up!

170
00:08:02,740 --> 00:08:03,780
What are these?

171
00:08:03,780 --> 00:08:04,580
These are...

172
00:08:04,580 --> 00:08:06,980
This seating is determined
by drawing lots.

173
00:08:06,980 --> 00:08:08,100
It's fair and square.

174
00:08:08,580 --> 00:08:09,660
As you can see,

175
00:08:09,660 --> 00:08:11,500
there are two red bamboo slips
in this draw.

176
00:08:11,980 --> 00:08:13,820
Whoever draws the red slip

177
00:08:13,820 --> 00:08:15,380
can sit next to the Crown Prince.

178
00:08:17,660 --> 00:08:18,660
This will definitely be mine.

179
00:08:19,260 --> 00:08:19,900
Interesting.

180
00:08:19,900 --> 00:08:20,860
So that's how it is.

181
00:08:22,140 --> 00:08:23,300
Then it will definitely be mine.

182
00:08:23,980 --> 00:08:25,660
So, does everyone understand now?

183
00:08:25,660 --> 00:08:26,660
- Yes.
- Yes.

184
00:08:26,660 --> 00:08:27,100
Come on,

185
00:08:27,100 --> 00:08:27,740
line up.

186
00:08:28,500 --> 00:08:29,220
Line up after me.

187
00:08:29,220 --> 00:08:29,980
I'll go first.

188
00:08:29,980 --> 00:08:30,980
- I'll go first.
- Don't push.

189
00:08:33,140 --> 00:08:35,060
- The red one.
- The red one.

190
00:08:35,060 --> 00:08:36,540
- You got it on the first try.
- You got it.

191
00:08:36,860 --> 00:08:38,580
- The red one.
- No luck.

192
00:08:39,620 --> 00:08:40,180
Go for it.

193
00:08:41,500 --> 00:08:42,420
Heaven is envious of talents.

194
00:08:43,300 --> 00:08:44,060
Without saying anything else,

195
00:08:45,740 --> 00:08:46,940
I don't think it's happening.

196
00:08:50,700 --> 00:08:51,620
What are you doing?

197
00:08:51,620 --> 00:08:53,900
I noticed that the one
you just drew wasn't red.

198
00:08:53,900 --> 00:08:55,060
I want to help you out.

199
00:08:56,780 --> 00:08:58,860
Later, you should...

200
00:08:58,860 --> 00:08:59,900
It's my turn.

201
00:09:00,860 --> 00:09:02,500
I haven't taken my hand out yet.

202
00:09:02,580 --> 00:09:04,540
Sorry. I was too eager.

203
00:09:06,260 --> 00:09:07,420
Are you cheating?

204
00:09:07,660 --> 00:09:08,900
Do you have something in your hand?

205
00:09:08,900 --> 00:09:09,660
No.

206
00:09:09,660 --> 00:09:10,380
Show me.

207
00:09:14,140 --> 00:09:14,820
This one.

208
00:09:15,300 --> 00:09:16,100
Now, I...

209
00:09:16,580 --> 00:09:18,020
Watch me later.

210
00:09:18,820 --> 00:09:20,380
Okay, I will.

211
00:09:24,420 --> 00:09:25,860
Did you hide it in your clothes?

212
00:09:41,740 --> 00:09:43,180
You must have hidden it in the shoe.

213
00:09:52,620 --> 00:09:54,620
Miss Su, are you done checking me?

214
00:09:54,620 --> 00:09:55,740
If you are, it's my turn.

215
00:10:01,380 --> 00:10:02,380
Don't let her get it.

216
00:10:02,660 --> 00:10:03,740
Don't let her get it.

217
00:10:03,940 --> 00:10:06,700
Sorry, I got it in the end, Miss Su.

218
00:10:10,260 --> 00:10:12,300
Now there are people on both sides.

219
00:10:12,460 --> 00:10:13,420
Now it's symmetrical, right?

220
00:10:13,420 --> 00:10:15,180
Isn't the scenery better here?

221
00:10:15,300 --> 00:10:16,260
Besides,

222
00:10:16,260 --> 00:10:17,460
I actually want to sit in the front.

223
00:10:19,260 --> 00:10:21,140
This seat is too far back.

224
00:10:21,700 --> 00:10:23,300
What luck do I have?

225
00:10:23,300 --> 00:10:25,540
I just happened to draw it.

226
00:10:25,660 --> 00:10:27,020
Don't get too excited too soon.

227
00:10:27,540 --> 00:10:29,020
How about finding someone to trade with?

228
00:10:29,420 --> 00:10:30,060
Brother.

229
00:10:30,300 --> 00:10:31,140
Who wants to trade with me?

230
00:10:31,940 --> 00:10:32,660
How about you trade with me?

231
00:10:32,700 --> 00:10:33,580
Told you.

232
00:10:33,580 --> 00:10:34,420
No.

233
00:10:34,980 --> 00:10:35,820
Brother.

234
00:10:36,340 --> 00:10:37,420
Are you done yet?

235
00:10:37,580 --> 00:10:38,820
It's fine.

236
00:10:39,340 --> 00:10:40,380
All you can see is the Crown Prince.

237
00:10:40,820 --> 00:10:41,900
- Let's go.
- Go away.

238
00:10:43,900 --> 00:10:44,660
